OL,6,FA van driver who killed two
OL,7,Fpedestrians as he "raced the lights"
OL,8,Fin central Carlisle has been jailed
OL,9,Ffor 18 months.
OL,11,FMarc Large, 49, from Sunderland was
OL,12,Fconvicted of causing their deaths by
OL,13,Fcareless driving at Carlisle Crown
OL,14,FCourt last month.
OL,16,FTerry Abson, 62, died at the scene on
OL,17,FWest Tower Street in March 2021. His
OL,18,Fpartner, Gina Lands, 56, passed away
OL,19,Fin hospital seven days later.
