OL,6,FLarge did not give evidence during his
OL,7,Ftrial. He had provided a prepared
OL,8,Fstatement when interviewed, saying
OL,9,Fthat his visual field was affected by
OL,10,Fglaring sun and recalling that he
OL,11,Fcarried out emergency stop braking. He
OL,12,Fdenied being distracted and had
OL,13,Fstated: "I really can't explain how
OL,14,Fthis collision occurred as I never saw
OL,15,Fthe couple until a split second before
OL,16,FI hit them."
