OL,6,FHarley Abson said: "My father was a
OL,7,Fkind and jolly man, with a near iron
OL,8,Fwill; nearly always happy, with a
OL,9,Fgreat big, often mischievous smile
OL,10,Fthat could light up any room.
OL,12,F"My mother was loving, wilful,
OL,13,Fcreative, and rather imaginative. When
OL,14,FI was younger she would create her own
OL,15,Fbedtime stories to tell me and others
OL,16,Fwhen there was a sleepover with our
OL,17,Fneighbours at the time.
