OL,6,F"This incident has naturally been the
OL,7,Fworst and hardest time in my life, and
OL,8,Fprobably will remain as such until the
OL,9,Ftime I depart myself.
OL,11,F"At the very least I would hope it is,
OL,12,Fas I cannot imagine what could be
OL,13,Fworse. I've lost my parents, my best
OL,14,Ffriends, my confidants, and in large
OL,15,Fparts my ambition and motivation. So
OL,16,Fmuch of my life revolved around them;
OL,17,Feven my hobbies were, in part, enjoyed
OL,18,Fthrough being able to share them with
OL,19,Fmy parents."
